## Anti-Patterns to Avoid

### ❌ Planning Failures

| Anti-Pattern | Problem | Fix |
|--------------|---------|-----|
| **Assumption-driven** | "I assumed you wanted X" | Ask before planning |
| **Vague todos** | "Implement auth" | "Add POST /api/login with OAuth2" |
| **No file paths** | "Update components" | "Modify src/components/AuthForm.tsx" |
| **Skipping approval** | Starting before user confirms | Always wait for explicit approval |
| **Over-engineering** | 20 todos for a toggle button | Simplicity first (Karpathy) |

### ❌ Execution Failures

| Anti-Pattern | Problem | Fix |
|--------------|---------|-----|
| **Serial when parallel works** | 5 agents running one-by-one | Launch independent agents together |
| **Unclear prompts** | "Fix the auth stuff" | "Implement login.ts per plan.md#todo-3" |
| **No verification** | Assuming agents succeeded | Check outputs, run tests, review code |
| **Agent sprawl** | 10 agents for a simple task | Use direct tools for simple work |

